Evgenia Simonova ("lusty"), Boris Shcherbakov ("White Festival"), Nicholas Shepherds ("Lady Macbeth of the Mtsensk District") in the melodrama "The wedding day will have to clarify." 

The film is about love, about the complex human relationships in a family where the well-being of the family suddenly explodes after son brings home a married woman. A movie that will make you empathize with the characters in the film, to suffer, to love, to live their lives.
